---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="AI/Data Literacy Consulting">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Header -->
        <header class="mb-20">
            <div
                class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-accent-terra font-mono mb-4"
            >
                <a
                    href={import.meta.env.BASE_URL === "/"
                        ? "/paths"
                        : import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "/paths"}
                    class="hover:text-text-primary transition-colors"
                    >&larr; Back to Paths</a
                >
                <span>/</span>
                <span>Primary Strategy</span>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold leading-none mb-8">
                AI & Data Literacy <br />
                <span class="text-accent-sage">Training & Consulting</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-2xl opacity-70 leading-relaxed">
                Leveraging 17+ years of information leadership to bridge the gap
                between complex data technologies and human workflow.
            </p>
        </header>

        <!-- 1. The Opportunity -->
        <section class="mb-24">
            <h2
                class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 border-b border-text-primary/10 pb-4"
            >
                01. The Opportunity
            </h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-4">Market Context</h3>
                    <p class="opacity-80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Global demand for AI literacy is outpacing supply.
                        Corporate budgets are shifting rapidly toward upskilling
                        teams on LLM workflows and data decision-making.
                    </p>
                    <ul
                        class="list-disc list-outside ml-4 space-y-2 opacity-80"
                    >
                        <li>
                            Vision 2030 initiatives in the Gulf requiring
                            digital fluency.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Finance sectors needing rapid dashboarding and
                            insight generation.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Information professionals seeking to reinvent their
                            value proposition.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-4 text-accent-terra">
                        Why Now?
                    </h3>
                    <p class="opacity-80 leading-relaxed">
                        The adoption curve of Generative AI has created an
                        "unfreezing" moment in organizational behavior.
                        Institutions are uniquely open to external expertise
                        that can demystify these tools without overpromising.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 2. Positioning -->
        <section
            class="mb-24 bg-white/50 p-12 -mx-12 border-l-4 border-accent-sage"
        >
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">02. Strategic Positioning</h2>
            <p class="text-xl mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                Most competitors are either <span class="italic"
                    >pure technologists</span
                > (too technical for business users) or <span class="italic"
                    >generalist trainers</span
                > (lacking deep data chops).
            </p>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">The Librarian Edge</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm opacity-70">
                        Deep expertise in information literacy, taxonomy, and
                        research ethics. Translating "search" to "prompt
                        engineering."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Technical Chops</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm opacity-70">
                        Tableau certified, Power BI fluent, Python capable. Can
                        actually build what is being taught.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Executive Presence</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm opacity-70">
                        Proven track record with QIA and Georgetown. Delivering
                        complex content to senior stakeholders.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 3. The Hybrid Model -->
        <section class="mb-24">
            <h2
                class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 border-b border-text-primary/10 pb-4"
            >
                03. The Hybrid Operating Model
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-12">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-32 flex-shrink-0 pt-2">
                        <span class="block text-accent-sage font-bold text-lg"
                            >Phase 1</span
                        >
                        <span class="text-sm opacity-50">Current</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">
                            Foundation & Verification
                        </h3>
                        <p class="opacity-80 mb-4">
                            Maintain full-time institutional role while building
                            portfolio via high-impact pilots (e.g., QIA). Focus
                            on curriculum development and initial case studies.
                        </p>
                        <div
                            class="bg-gray-100 px-4 py-2 inline-block text-sm font-mono"
                        >
                            Target: 1-2 Major Workshops / Year
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                >
                    <div class="w-full md:w-32 flex-shrink-0 pt-2">
                        <span class="block text-text-primary font-bold text-lg"
                            >Phase 2</span
                        >
                        <span class="text-sm opacity-50">Growth</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">
                            Expansion & Scale
                        </h3>
                        <p class="opacity-80 mb-4">
                            Potential negotiation for reduced institutional
                            hours or accumulated leave to accommodate larger
                            contracts. Expansion into APAC network.
                        </p>
                        <div
                            class="bg-gray-100 px-4 py-2 inline-block text-sm font-mono"
                        >
                            Target: Quarterly Engagements
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                >
                    <div class="w-full md:w-32 flex-shrink-0 pt-2">
                        <span class="block text-text-primary font-bold text-lg"
                            >Phase 3</span
                        >
                        <span class="text-sm opacity-50">Pivot</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Independence</h3>
                        <p class="opacity-80 mb-4">
                            Full transition to independent practice, leveraging
                            established client base and reputation. Optional:
                            Retain academic affiliation as adjunct/fellow.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 4. Success & Risks -->
        <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-24">
            <div class="bg-bg-sage border border-text-primary/10 p-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6">Success Markers</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-accent-sage mr-2">✔</span>
                        <span class="leading-tight"
                            >Recurring revenue contracts (Retainers vs One-offs)</span
                        >
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-accent-sage mr-2">✔</span>
                        <span class="leading-tight"
                            >Invitation to speak at key industry conferences
                            (Singapore, Dubai)</span
                        >
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-accent-sage mr-2">✔</span>
                        <span class="leading-tight"
                            >Referral network generating inbound leads</span
                        >
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-bg-sage border border-red-900/10 p-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-red-900/80">
                    Key Risks
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-red-900/60 mr-2">⚠</span>
                        <span class="leading-tight"
                            ><strong>Burnout:</strong> Managing two full-time workloads.
                            Requires strict boundary management.</span
                        >
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-red-900/60 mr-2">⚠</span>
                        <span class="leading-tight"
                            ><strong>Conflict of Interest:</strong> Ensuring side
                            work does not breach Georgetown policies.</span
                        >
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
